#Before proceeding with what is an ids?
##learn what is an intruder

###Intruder
An intruder is an unauthorized person who is trying to break into your network without your perimission ,without your knowldege with a criminal/
mischivieous mindset and actions performed by such user is known as intrusion
###Types of Intruders
There are tow types of intruders 
Outside intruders(Masquerader)-- intruders without any authorisation of the system trying to get into the system are called out outside intruders
.These try to steal or get the neccessary credentials that is required to get into the system.
They can use various attacks like phising,malware etc.But can be detected by firewall

Inside intruders(Misfeasor)-- intruders which are legitimate and have partial authorisation of the system because they are the part of the system 
or lets say authorisation of some parts but thye try to misues their privliges to exploit,steal or sell the data.These are harder to detect or 
or catch and are more dangerous than the outside intruders or misquereaders

##IDS(INTRUSION DETECTION SYSTEM)
A ids detects the chages over network and look for so unauthoriused work going on. It works in the background and whenever it detects any changes
it informs the system administrator or network adminitrator.It is software that checks a network or system for malicious activities or policy 
violations.
